    "Based nowhere in particular — currently in {city}. I've set up for async-first communication so timezones usually don't matter, but I'll give you a clear window when I'm reachable." : {
      "comment" : "Example — call availability",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Based nowhere in particular — currently in {city}. I've set up for async-first communication so timezones usually don't matter, but I'll give you a clear window when I'm reachable."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tidak berbasis di tempat tertentu — saat ini di {city}. Saya sudah mengatur komunikasi async-first sehingga zona waktu biasanya tidak masalah, tapi saya akan memberi tahu jendela waktu yang jelas saat saya bisa dihubungi."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "정해진 거점은 없고 — 지금은 {city}에 있습니다. 비동기 우선 커뮤니케이션 환경으로 타임존이 큰 문제가 되지 않지만, 연락 가능한 시간대는 명확히 알려드리겠습니다."
          }
        }
      }
    },
