    "Hi {client_name}, I noticed you're hiring for {role}. I've worked on similar projects for {reference} — here's a quick overview: {portfolio}. Open to a 15-min chat?" : {
      "comment" : "Example — upwork proposal",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Hi {client_name}, I noticed you're hiring for {role}. I've worked on similar projects for {reference} — here's a quick overview: {portfolio}. Open to a 15-min chat?"
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Halo {client_name}, saya melihat Anda merekrut untuk {role}. Saya telah mengerjakan proyek serupa untuk {reference} — berikut ringkasannya: {portfolio}. Bersedia ngobrol 15 menit?"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "안녕하세요 {client_name}님, {role} 포지션 채용 중이신 것을 보았습니다. {reference}에서 비슷한 프로젝트를 진행한 경험이 있으며 — 간단한 포트폴리오: {portfolio}. 15분 정도 짧은 대화 가능할까요?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hi {client}, giving you a heads-up — {reason}, so I'm pushing the delivery to {new_date}. I'll send a progress preview tomorrow so you're not left in the dark." : {
      "comment" : "Example — delay",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Hi {client}, giving you a heads-up — {reason}, so I'm pushing the delivery to {new_date}. I'll send a progress preview tomorrow so you're not left in the dark."
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Halo {client}, saya beri tahu sebelumnya — {reason}, jadi saya menunda pengiriman ke {new_date}. Saya akan mengirim pratinjau progress besok sehingga Anda tidak ketinggalan informasi."
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "안녕하세요 {client}님, 미리 알려드립니다 — {reason}으로 인해 납기를 {new_date}로 연기합니다. 진행 상황은 내일 미리 보여드려 답답하지 않도록 하겠습니다."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hi {client}, happy to take this on — it falls outside our original scope ({original_scope}), so I'll send an updated quote for this add-on. Does that work?" : {
      "comment" : "Example — scope pushback",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Hi {client}, happy to take this on — it falls outside our original scope ({original_scope}), so I'll send an updated quote for this add-on. Does that work?"
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Halo {client}, saya senang menerima ini — namun ini di luar lingkup awal kita ({original_scope}), jadi saya akan mengirim penawaran yang diperbarui untuk tambahan ini. Apakah itu OK?"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "안녕하세요 {client}님, 기꺼이 도와드리겠습니다 — 다만 원래 스코프({original_scope})를 벗어나는 작업이라 업데이트된 견적을 보내드리겠습니다. 괜찮을까요?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
