          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hi {client}, if you enjoyed working together, a short testimonial (2–3 sentences) for my site would mean a lot. No pressure at all — only if it's easy." : {
      "comment" : "Example — testimonial",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
